# Event RSVP outreach (public Comms)

## Product insights (locked)

- **Real LEC job:** hybrid meetings (on site + remote). Officers need **two numbers**: quorum = Yes (either mode); **food heads** = on-site Yes + guests only.
- **Calendar Accept/Decline cannot do this** — native invite RSVP has no on-site vs remote. Use copy-only email + Excel (R0) or token form (R1).
- **Sample invite email = public tool**, not Hub. Announcement class, no member PII, copy-only / `mailto:`. Grievance drafts stay in Hub (MFA + audit).
- **No auto-send** for this Comms path. Footer must say review-before-send / no collection.
- **Hub officer reminder draft (R2)** is a **different** builder (`membership-meeting-reminder.ts`) on the Events board — do not merge into `event-email.ts` or put invite copy on grievance draft APIs. See `.cursor/rules/calendar-meetings.mdc` and `docs/audit/current-ground-truth.md`.

